ype":"message","text":"Although there is interesting reason why it's this way in Poland. From ERC grant you get paid same amount you are paid at the same position/level at your university. Which means in Poland, person up to few (typically up to ~6-8 years) after PhD gets around 4000 PLN/month (but sometimes less) after taxes which is ~900 EUR/1100 USD.","user":"US8Q0Q98W","ts":"1608216077.086700","team":"T68168MUP","blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"JBY","elements":[{"type":"rich_text_section","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"Although there is interesting reason why it's this way in Poland. From ERC grant you get paid same amount you are paid at the same position/level at your university. Which means in Poland, person up to few (typically up to ~6-8 years) after PhD gets around 4000 PLN/month (but sometimes less) after taxes which is ~900 EUR/1100 USD."}]}]}],"thread_ts":"1608039601.064900","parent_user_id":"UDB26738Q"},{"client_msg_id":"09521a1d-6be5-46c0-9325-6221bfe6fbe8","type":"message","text":"That's the reason why many people don't bother with writing ERC grants in Poland. I suppose it's quite similar for rest of Eastern Europe. Because you get a lot of extra (non-science, grand writing and administrative) work and responsibility and you don't get paid for it. If they introduced rule to _whatever's higher_ of _*average European wage*_ or local payment at the university then perhaps we would see more applications form Eastern Europe.","user":"US8Q0Q98W","ts":"1608216371.086900","team":"T68168MUP","blocks":[{"type":"rich_text","block_id":"7qX","elements":[{"type":"rich_text_section","elements":[{"type":"text","text":"That's the reason why many people don't bother with writing ERC grants in Poland. I suppose it's quite similar for rest of Eastern Europe. Because you get a lot of extra (non-science, grand writing and administrative) work and responsibility and you don't get paid for it. If they introduced rule to "},{"type":"text","text":"whatever's higher","style":{"italic":true}},{"type":"text","text":" of "},{"type":"text","text":"average European wage","style":{"bold":true,"italic":true}},{"type":"text","text":" or local payment at the university then perhaps we would see more applications form Eastern Europe."}]}]}],"thread_ts":"1608039601.064900","parent_user_id":"UDB26738Q"}]